snippet.title: 逆光迷途 Lost in Darklight - Trailer
snippet.description:
Themed on urban suspense, Lost in Darklight is a live action interactive game. A retired ace soldier, four girls, a hidden chamber at home, genetic cloning tech... Experience interactive VR panoramic evidence searching with this game and decide your own ending. Every choice you make is crucial!

Developper : Beijing Changyou Chuangxiang Software Technology Co., Ltd.
Publisher : Changyou.com HK Limited
